- `artifacts/dmd_processed/reports/metrics.json`
- `artifacts/dmd_processed/tflite/model_float32.tflite`
- `artifacts/dmd_processed/tflite/model_int8.tflite`
- ejemplo Android: `android_inference_example.kt`
